Type: Package
Package: fundsr
Title: Rolling Differences (CAGR and Log) and Liquidity for UCITS ETFs; Survival and Other Financial Planning Plots
Version: 0.2.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Stanislav", "Traykov", , "st@gmuf.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A small tidyverse-based framework for importing and plotting
    UCITS ETF and index data, ETF liquidity measures, as well as survival curves and other
    plots related to financial planning.
